{"tid":652032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港史上首位「暴動罪」耆英——Sam哥無悔2016年旺角初一夜站在前線","createTime":"2018-05-03T14:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T07:40:22.000Z","uid":28366,"like":95,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"53929c9a26494fee5649d45dd63242e4ba14cb7a","tid":652032,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"有關當晚的事件，留在大眾的印象都是零星的混亂場面，甚至認為是一班廢青染上了網上勇武的風氣而鬧事，鮮為人知的是其中一位暴動罪被告已踏古稀之年，這不禁令人想起電影《十年》中的自焚者是個阿婆，他們亦正是第一代的香港人，一個經歷過香港逃難、落地生根、見證過繁盛，最後家園仍面臨再次被毀，這種自焚的控訴，恰如輪迴中的咆哮。<br />\n<br />\n旺角初一當晚，到底發生了一件怎樣的事？我們嘗試透過參予其中的人物重塑事件......<br />\n<br />\nSam哥目前已被判暴動罪成、還柙等候判刑。<br />\n<br />\n在去年九月首次訪問Sam哥後，筆者曾與好友談起Sam哥，朋友一聽到這位暴動罪被告已逾七十，馬上問：「他有沒有家人、仔女？經濟狀況好嗎？」筆者回答，其實Sam哥是退休裁縫，三代同堂，有一仔兩女、四名孫兒女，住在黃大仙的中產屋苑。Sam哥絕非「廢青」，也不是「撈唔掂」。<br />\n<br />\nSam哥是老一輩的香港「獅子山下」故事中的成功者：逃難來港，受益於香港黃金年代，白手興家、業有專精、事業成功，本可安享清福，就是因為關心政治，感受到現在的「倒退」，在退休後更站在前線，參與本土派抗爭，終致身受「暴動罪」政治檢控，以高齡之身，或面臨多年囚禁的厄運。他最大的心願，是大家團結守護香港本土。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/05/sam-gor-interview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F05%2Fsam-gor-interview%2F&d=NSF48g5z55m58eGwmoQUIjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5e7f7086\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/05/sam-gor-interview/</a>"},{"pid":"a42728cda5ef4e9cd0ddc5e42a5b238366cc6bd9","tid":652032,"uid":171107,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"啲落井下石既花生友知唔知醜"},{"pid":"368bdc255ecc9c5a0d69c7efbe652b68802c4547","tid":652032,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6273e92ca743f9e22d4f40a17f6a9ae7ca073c75","tid":652032,"uid":104443,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共匪必須被消滅！為咗香港嘅未來，我地要團結一致支持國府反攻大陸！中華民國先係正統中國！中華民國必將統一中國！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f42428c36097de82a4ef9cb3ce00407f13a8d796","tid":652032,"uid":28366,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/222500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F222500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=08ecc428&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc6961a8fd97808bb9b2de8216c9b68596c2a437","tid":652032,"uid":19501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"70歲人為咗香港坐幾年監，到呢個年紀我只會係苟且偷安緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564be81f0b1f87b31d358e4ca16c711311210f00","tid":652032,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11675fe3bcdcbf4a39e9d3a63d95ee3366e91e9f","tid":652032,"uid":99205,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"fc6961a8fd97808bb9b2de8216c9b68596c2a437","tid":652032,"uid":19501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"70歲人為咗香港坐幾年監，到呢個年紀我只會係苟且偷安緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:37:49.000Z","msg":"唔好再俾D五毛分化到<br />\n<br />\n從前係大陸來但努力勤辛既一樣係好既真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ca8167a367176e575e85e5f5e4769a8b9a9d38","tid":652032,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"長毛出黎叫佢收皮未"},{"pid":"e2e2e20cf24cd1d694d994b9460c3141fd04b18b","tid":652032,"uid":51859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11675fe3bcdcbf4a39e9d3a63d95ee3366e91e9f","tid":652032,"uid":99205,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"fc6961a8fd97808bb9b2de8216c9b68596c2a437","tid":652032,"uid":19501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score"